#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Resource Method records the method that was executed.\n"
"We can check if the Resource Method was executed as expected by the HTTP Method and URI."
msgstr "O “Resource Method” registra o método que foi executado. Podemos verificar se o “Resource Method” foi executado conforme o esperado, com base no método HTTP e na URI."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
